{"tid":1308858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【水貨客之災】屈錢搶電話 上水拉麵店大戰水貨客七年 老闆：做到好灰","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T00:03:43.000Z","uid":18391,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddaec6f40b5b4db30bd10d7eb9ef8526f059156","tid":1308858,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/etw/magazine/article/20180723/3_58467495/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fetw%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F3_58467495%2F&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0DFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=02bd05ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fetw%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F3_58467495%2F&h=3e00fb04\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/etw/magazine/article/20180723/3_58467495/</a><br />\n<br />\n做生意，大家都是擔心生意不夠，賺不了錢，交不到租。但如果店鋪開在上水區，你還要多擔心一個問題&mdash;&mdash;水貨客。上水區因為鄰近關口，藥房、化妝品店林立，四輪行李箱快要多過路上汽車。在上水橫巷中生存了七年的麵家山下更是見證着區內變遷，亦成為當中的受害者。「水貨客會在店鋪前執貨，阻礙門口，亦有很多投訴。」老闆黃生說。起初黃生年少氣盛，會和他們爭論，經年月洗禮，棱角終被磨平，處事變得圓滑，但仍抱住堅持，「為了家人，頂硬上。」<br />\n採訪：黎芷縈<br />\n攝影：王暐彤<br />\n麵家山下<br />\n地址：上水新康街63號地下D3-D4號鋪<br />\n營業時間：星期一至日12nn-3pm, 6pm-9pm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日去上水食拉麵啦"},{"pid":"55508abf6298686401fec21f69cbc48877518737","tid":1308858,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"條街有後生七日仙個個星期換<br />\n<br />\n快d去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239164737cee6f711606742a58ea763516a0dd29","tid":1308858,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T00:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6022d0f8274f0cda3329183e0e8499b9d9e92831","tid":1308858,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T00:03:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31789b778ddd2d